# right-outer-to-inner-le

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `join_transformation_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (filter (le ?col ?val) (join right-outer ?cond ?left ?right))
rhs: (filter (le ?col ?val) (join inner ?cond ?left ?right))
